comments: Anuniby (TOR) cleanly steals the ball away from Embiid (PHI).
Horford (PHI) cleanly blocks Anunoby's (TOR) driving shot attempt.
As Gasol (TOR) is attempting to retrieve the loose ball, he makes incidental contact with Embiid's (PHI) arm. Gasol immediately releases his arm from Embiid.
Anunoby (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position on Simmons (PHI) during the drive as his arms remain collapsed against his body not delivering contact to Simmons.
Anunoby (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Richardson (PHI).
Gasol (TOR) legally blocks Embiid's (PHI) driving shot attempt as when he swipes down, he makes clean contact with the ball.
Horford (PHI) is in a legal screening position and does not deliver contact to VanVleet (TOR).
Embiid (PHI) makes contact to the body of Siakam (TOR) during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.

Powell (TOR) moves legally alongside of Harris (PHI) getting his right arm in a vertical position as Harris moves back into Powell's legal right vertical arm initiating contact during the driving shot attempt.
Siakam (TOR) and Embiid (PHI) engage and disengage while rebounding.
Richardson (PHI) maintains a legal guarding position as he moves alongside VanVleet's (TOR) path and does not deliver contact.
VanVleet (TOR) briefly engages with Horford (PHI) as Horford is setting the screen, but immediately disengages sliding his hands off.
Richardson (PHI) commits a personal take foul on VanVleet (TOR).
Powell (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Harris (PHI).
Simmons (PHI) and Powell (TOR) make incidental contact with each other as the two are attempting to retrieve the rebound.
